@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBackgroundColor #F3E5F5
skinparam classBorderColor #6A1B9A
[*] --> Approved
Approved --> Processing : reject
Processing --> OnHold : cancel
Processing : entry / log card
OnHold --> Cancelled : reject
Cancelled --> Closed : review
Closed --> Archived : reject
Archived --> [*]
@enduml